PRIVACY POLICY
This privacy policy was last updated on June 1, 2022.
Thank you for visiting the Global DRO website and reviewing our privacy policy (“Privacy Policy”). We are committed to ensuring that your privacy is protected. This website globaldro.com and the associated Global DRO platform (both together, the “Platform”) is operated by a partnership between the Canadian Centre for Ethics in Sport, Swiss Sport Integrity, UK Anti-Doping, the United States Anti-Doping Agency, the Japan Anti-Doping Agency, Sport Integrity Australia, and Sport Integrity Commission NZ (all together, referred to as “Global DRO”).
Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. By continuing to use the Platform, you agree to have your personal information handled in the manner described in this Privacy Policy.
